Setup
=====
> mv config.ex.php config.php
> mv sqlite.ex.sql3 sqlite.sql3

Make sure you edit config.php with the proper values, registration is disabled by default.

Note
====
This is not currently usable in a production environment, here is a list of todos:
* Hash password with bcrypt
* Check if email is in use
* Add captchas to login, or after 3 failures
* Add captcha to registration
